<h1 style="text-transform:none">OpenBD Engine</h1>

<p>
The OpenBlueDragon engine is shipped as a standard J2EE WAR (Web ARchive) application.  This a standard packaging mechanism that is defined
that allows any J2EE supporting application server to easily and quickly run.
</p>

<p>
OpenBlueDragon is shipped in a number of formats, but they all derive from this standard WAR format.  The most popular download
is the pre-bundled Ready-To-Run Jetty installation, that has OpenBlueDragon already ready to run.
</p>

